node.text:
The colours of the Outback… 🧡❤️💜 Which one is your favourite? >>>> Sunsets here are a special experience in themselves, as the sun goes down this entire landscape comes alive and begins to glow deep burnt oranges and reds — On our road trip we stumbled upon these rock formations just outside of Mount Isa and fell in love with watching the changing colours of this landscape. @queensland @britzcampervans #thisisqueensland 

#outbackqueensland #outbackqldmagicmoments

node.text:
Rising desert moon… ✨🌙 🧡 Last month I had the chance to explore the hidden gems of the outback with an adventure throughout North West Queensland >>>>> 

A part of @outbackqueensland which has always intrigued me, we ventured out on a 10 day road trip to experience a one-of-a-kind nomadic adventure. North West Queensland is full of so much beauty, wandering throughout the changing colours of the landscape and spent nights living off grid under the starry skies (the best way to explore up here!) — I’m very grateful to see more of my homeland, lots more to share over the coming weeks. @queensland @britzcampervans #thisisqueensland 

#outbackqueensland #outbackqldmagicmoments #mountisa

 #discovertasmania #momentsinthewild #comedownforair

node.text:
Blue hour hiking through the raw wilderness of South West Tasmania…✨💙 I’m thrilled to be announcing my ambassadorship with @merrellaustralia – Sharing my journey in nature and experiencing more outdoor adventures together! We want to enable everyone to feel adventurous, empowered and like they belong while being outdoors & exploring our beautiful planet – I’ve never felt so grateful to be able to spend more time in nature and look forward to sharing this adventure with you! #MerrellAustralia ⁣#Createyourtrail #OutdoorAdventures

@tasmania #tassieoffseason

Changing of seasons… ✨🌞🍂 In the depths of @tasmania – A palette of deep burnt oranges and warm golden tones throughout a landscape filled with button grass plains and majestic mountain peaks. A series captured throughout the highlands of Tassie, just as winter sets in. #tassieoffseason 

#discovertasmania #momentsinthewild #comedownforair

node.text:
Slow moments along the East Coast of @tasmania…✨🌾🌈☁️ Endless blue horizons, golden grasses, sea-shells & long beautiful beaches @eastcoasttasmania 

Captured during my stay @piermont. This part of Tassie has such a special feeling and in winter offers a completely different Australian coastal experience. #tassieoffseason 

#discovertasmania #momentsinthewild #comedownforair

Rising moon…✨🌙☁️
>>>> A series of moments in the wild throughout @tasmania 
Amongst the depths of nature, clouds dancing throughout the sky, fresh mountain air, light beaming in the darkness, a constant ebb and flow of interconnections. 

#tassieoffseason  #discovertasmania #momentsinthewild #comedownforair

The wind-swept coastlines of King Island, Tasmania…✨☁️🌾
Listen to stories of the land, dream deeply – when you take your time to slow down in Tassie you’ll witness the Off Season in a different light. @kittawalodge @tasmania @visitnorthwesttasmania #tassieoffseason 

#discovertasmania #tasmania #australia #kingIsland #travel #comedownforair

Forever a lover of the sea… ✨🌊 The vastness of the horizons, the depths of the unknown and the crashing sound of the waves along the shoreline. A place where the sky and the sea meet. Here’s a little collection from various sea-side locations around Tassie. Lots more new stories to come! 

@tasmania @satelliteisland @satelliteislandtasmania #discovertasmania #tassieoffseason

Namibia has my heart…💛 
PHOTOGRAPHY COMPETITION –  I’m excited to be announcing a chance to win a once in a lifetime TRIP FOR 2 TO NAMIBIA in partnership with @wild.ark @ehranamibia & @nuii_icecream_global 
 
We are looking for your most creative travel photos, taken off the beaten track. Somewhere wilder than the everyday – A unique and unexpected moment in a unique and unexpected place. It could be your favourite travel memory or something completely new you discovered on your doorstep. 
 
This is a special opportunity to join a conservation adventure and a desert elephant expedition and learn first hand about the critically-endangered desert elephant population. Expect to get your hands dirty, learn about conservation, make new friends, sleep under the stars and enjoy the natural, beautiful surroundings. 
 
Each year @nuii_icecream_global is committed to supporting biodiversity projects in wild places where they can make a real difference to the lives of people & animals as well as their environment. Wild places are a huge source of inspiration for us and it’s important we give back in some way. 
 
I can’t wait to see what you guys create and help to choose the winner – check my Stories for the link & head to the @nuii_icecream_global to read the full terms and conditions and find out more about this opportunity! Good Luck! 

#MyNuiiAdventure #IceCreamAdventure
